1. *Odavno* sam zaboravio tvoje ime. (I had forgotten your name long ago.) 
2. On je odavno napustio ovu zemlju. (He had left this country a long time ago.)
3. *Odavno* nismo videli jedno drugo. (We hadn't seen each other for a long time.)
4. Ona je *odavno* ušla u penziju. (She had retired a long time ago.)
5. *Odavno* se nismo čuli. (We hadn't been in touch for a long time.)
6. *Odavno* se zna da je ona zaljubljena. (It has been known for a long time that she is in love.)